    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1 H3C LA2608 室内无线网关用户手册",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            90,
            61,
            611,
            84
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1.1 概述",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            90,
            102,
            196,
            122
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "H3C LA2608-GM/GU 室内无线网关（以下简称 LA2608）可以为用户提供无线服务，为了实现对设备的管理，LA2608 需要通过 3G/4G 网络连接到运营商无线控制器。",
        "bbox": [
            141,
            138,
            907,
            174
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/07645668bfab67e81bac47a7c5f603401426be1b3216242f586546808fc27dab.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            146,
            188,
            184,
            212
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "说明",
        "bbox": [
            188,
            198,
            223,
            212
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "目前，LA2608 只支持与 H3C 公司的无线控制器互通。",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            224,
            561,
            239
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1.2 配置LA2608与无线控制器互通",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            90,
            282,
            484,
            302
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "如 图 1 所示，LA2608 安装了SIM卡，通过 3G/4G网络连接到运营商无线控制器，并向用户提供无线服务。关于LA2608的安装方法，请参见“H3C LA2608室内无线网关 快速安装指南”。",
        "bbox": [
            141,
            320,
            907,
            355
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/25307ddba26964ba7daa9dc6a1251a551313cc2a981ab84e8f9c0a0814a016fa.jpg",
        "image_caption": [
            "图1 配置 LA2608 与无线控制器互通"
        ],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            147,
            390,
            811,
            584
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1.2.1 配置LA2608",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            90,
            625,
            260,
            642
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1) 配置拨号访问组的拨号控制列表",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            659,
            438,
            675
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "<LA2608>system-view ",
        "guess_lang": "txt",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            682,
            310,
            695
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "[LA2608]dialer-rule 1 ip permit ",
        "guess_lang": "txt",
        "bbox": [
            146,
            699,
            413,
            713
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2) 配置 DCC 拨号",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            716,
            305,
            732
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/39057cd15c7479a2fd918c53f2da062a7b3267cb4e170eaca2cd78b335a1f787.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            146,
            748,
            184,
            770
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "说明",
        "bbox": [
            188,
            756,
            225,
            771
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "dialer number命令用来配置发起呼叫的拨号串，不同运营商的拨号串不同，请用户在配置前向网络运营商获取发起呼叫的拨号串。",
        "bbox": [
            141,
            781,
            907,
            815
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "[LA2608]interface Cellular-Ethernet2/0  \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]ip address cellular-allocated  \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer enable-circular  \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer-group 1  \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer timer idle 0 ",
        "guess_lang": "powershell",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            850,
            645,
            929
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "page_number",
        "text": "1 ",
        "bbox": [
            505,
            948,
            515,
            958
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer timer autodial 5  \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]dialer number *99# autodial  \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]nat outbound  \n[LA2608-Cellular-Ethernet2/0]quit ",
        "guess_lang": "powershell",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            51,
            626,
            115
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(3) 配置 DNS 解析功能",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            118,
            342,
            133
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "[LA2608]dns resolve ",
        "guess_lang": "txt",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            141,
            310,
            153
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(4) 配置静态路由",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            157,
            295,
            173
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "[LA2608]ip route-static 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 Cellular-Ethernet2/0 ",
        "guess_lang": "txt",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            181,
            660,
            194
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(5) 指定运营商无线控制器的 IP 地址",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            198,
            443,
            213
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "[LA2608] wlan ac ip 60.191.99.143 ",
        "guess_lang": "txt",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            220,
            428,
            233
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1.2.2 配置运营商无线控制器",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            90,
            248,
            352,
            264
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/8ca3c3627f4ec48e0ec841e036f5ba63e3476d2417c3e8a168e49f82496c18a8.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            144,
            290,
            184,
            313
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "说明",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            188,
            298,
            226,
            313
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "如下配置仅供参考，运营商可根据实际情况进行调整。",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            324,
            559,
            339
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1) 创建业务 VLAN",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            374,
            312,
            389
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "<AC>system-view  \n[AC]vlan 2  \n[AC-vlan2] quit ",
        "guess_lang": "objectivec",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            397,
            275,
            442
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2) 创建 WLAN-ESS 接口并加入业务 VLAN",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            447,
            500,
            461
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "[AC]interfaceWLAN-ESS1   \n[AC-WLAN-ESS1]portaccessvlan2   \n[AC-WLAN-ESS1]quit ",
        "guess_lang": "objectivec",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            471,
            421,
            516
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(3) 配置明文方式的服务模板",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            521,
            383,
            536
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "[AC]wlan service-template 1 clear  \n[AC-wlan-st-1]ssid ssidh3c  \n[AC-wlan-st-1]bind WLAN-ESS 1  \n[AC-wlan-st-1]service-template enable  \nPlease wait... Done.  \n[AC-wlan-st-1]quit ",
        "guess_lang": "txt",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            543,
            463,
            638
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(4) 开启自动 AP 功能",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            644,
            327,
            659
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "[AC]wlan auto-ap enable  \n[AC]wlan ap 2608 model LA2608 id 1  \n[AC-wlan-ap-2608]serial-id auto  \n[AC-wlan-ap-2608]radio 1  \n[AC-wlan-ap-2608-radio-1]service-template 1  \n[AC-wlan-ap-2608-radio-1]radio enable  \n[AC-wlan-ap-2608-radio-1]quit  \n[AC-wlan-ap-2608]quit ",
        "guess_lang": "objectivec",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            667,
            515,
            796
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(5) 配置 VLAN 接口 IP 地址",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            800,
            374,
            815
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "[AC]interface Vlan-interface 1   \n[AC-Vlan-interface1]ip address 60.191.99.143 255.255.0.0   \n[AC-Vlan-interface1]quit   \n[AC]interface Vlan-interface 2   \n[AC-Vlan-interface2]ip address 10.249.136.1 255.255.252.0   \n[AC-Vlan-interface2]quit ",
        "guess_lang": "txt",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            824,
            635,
            920
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(6) 使能 DHCP 服务，配置 DHCP 地址池 ",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            923,
            482,
            939
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "page_number",
        "text": "",
        "bbox": [
            505,
            948,
            515,
            958
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "[AC]dhcp enable  \n[AC]dhcp server ip-pool vlan2  \n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]network 10.249.136.0 22  \n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]gateway-list 10.249.136.1  \n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]dns-list 218.201.96.130  \n[AC-dhcp-pool-vlan1]quit ",
        "guess_lang": "txt",
        "bbox": [
            144,
            51,
            532,
            149
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "1.2.3 验证LA2608 与无线控制器是否连通",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            90,
            162,
            468,
            180
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "在无线控制器上执行 display wlan ap 命令，state 字段显示为“R/M”，表示 LA2608 与无线控制器之间已经建立连接。",
        "bbox": [
            141,
            195,
            907,
            229
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "code",
        "sub_type": "code",
        "code_caption": [],
        "code_body": "< Sysname> display wlan ap all  \nTotal Number of APs configured : 1  \nTotal Number of configured APs connected : 1  \nTotal Number of auto APs connected : 0  \nAP Profiles  \nState : I = Idle, J = Join, JA = JoinAck, IL = ImageLoad  \nC = Config, R = Run, KU = KeyUpdate, KC = KeyCfm  \nM = Master, B = Backup  \nAP Name State Model Serial-ID  \nap1 R/M LA2608 036286A054000033 ",
        "guess_lang": "txt",
        "bbox": [
            142,
            237,
            835,
            448
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
